    <content>
      <![CDATA[<blockquote><p>适用平台：Windows &#x2F; macOS &#x2F; Linux | 更新时间：2026-06</p></blockquote><hr><h2 id="一、什么是-OpenClaw"><a href="#一、什么是-OpenClaw" class="headerlink" title="一、什么是 OpenClaw"></a>一、什么是 OpenClaw</h2><p>OpenClaw 是一个本地 AI Agent 运行时。安装后可以通过 CLI（终端命令）、Web 控制台、或各种聊天平台（微信、Telegram、Discord 等）与 AI 对话，支持文件读写、命令执行、联网搜索、定时任务等工具。</p><p>核心组件：</p><table><thead><tr><th>组件</th><th>说明</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><strong>Gateway</strong></td><td>核心服务，管理会话、路由消息、执行工具</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Control UI</strong></td><td>浏览器控制台，<code>http://127.0.0.1:18789</code></td></tr><tr><td><strong>Channels</strong></td><td>消息渠道（微信&#x2F;Telegram&#x2F;Discord&#x2F;Slack 等）</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Skills</strong></td><td>社区能力模块，可安装扩展功能</td></tr></tbody></table><hr><h2 id="二、准备工作"><a href="#二、准备工作" class="headerlink" title="二、准备工作"></a>二、准备工作</h2><h3 id="2-1-系统要求"><a href="#2-1-系统要求" class="headerlink" title="2.1 系统要求"></a>2.1 系统要求</h3><ul><li>推荐<strong>Node.js 24</strong> 最低支持Node.js 22.19+</li><li>操作系统：Windows 10 &#x2F; Windows 11 &#x2F; macOS 12 Monterey 或更新版本 &#x2F; Linux</li><li>一个模型供应商的 API Key（见 2.2）</li></ul><p>查看 Node 版本：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">node --version</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>如果未安装或版本过低，从 <a href="https://nodejs.org/">nodejs.org</a> 下载安装。</p><h3 id="2-2-API-Key"><a href="#2-2-API-Key" class="headerlink" title="2.2 API Key"></a>2.2 API Key</h3><p>OpenClaw 本身不提供模型服务，需要接入第三方模型 API。常用选项：</p><table><thead><tr><th>供应商(主流模型)</th><th>获取方式</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><strong>DeepSeek(DeepSeek V4)</strong></td><td><a href="https://platform.deepseek.com/">platform.deepseek.com</a> → API Keys</td></tr><tr><td><strong>豆包(Doubao-Seed-2.0)</strong></td><td><a href="https://console.volcengine.com/">console.volcengine.com</a>→ 登录</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Anthropic(Claude Opus 4.6)</strong></td><td><a href="https://console.anthropic.com/">console.anthropic.com</a> → API Keys</td></tr><tr><td><strong>OpenAI(GPT-5.2)</strong></td><td><a href="https://platform.openai.com/">platform.openai.com</a> → API Keys</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Google(Gemini)</strong></td><td><a href="https://ai.google.dev/">ai.google.dev</a> → API Key</td></tr></tbody></table><hr><h2 id="三、安装-OpenClaw"><a href="#三、安装-OpenClaw" class="headerlink" title="三、安装 OpenClaw"></a>三、安装 OpenClaw</h2><h3 id="3-1-Windows（PowerShell）"><a href="#3-1-Windows（PowerShell）" class="headerlink" title="3.1 Windows（PowerShell）"></a>3.1 Windows（PowerShell）</h3><p>打开 PowerShell（管理员权限），执行：</p><figure class="highlight powershell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">iwr</span> <span class="literal">-useb</span> https://openclaw.ai/install.ps1 | <span class="built_in">iex</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>安装脚本会自动检测系统、安装 Node（如未安装）、安装 OpenClaw 并启动初次配置向导。</p><p>或者手动通过 npm 安装：</p><figure class="highlight powershell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install <span class="literal">-g</span> openclaw@latest</span><br><span class="line">openclaw onboard <span class="literal">--install-daemon</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="3-2-macOS-Linux-WSL2"><a href="#3-2-macOS-Linux-WSL2" class="headerlink" title="3.2 macOS &#x2F; Linux &#x2F; WSL2"></a>3.2 macOS &#x2F; Linux &#x2F; WSL2</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">curl -fsSL https://openclaw.ai/install.sh | bash</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="3-3-Docker（服务器部署）"><a href="#3-3-Docker（服务器部署）" class="headerlink" title="3.3 Docker（服务器部署）"></a>3.3 Docker（服务器部署）</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">docker run -d --name openclaw \</span><br><span class="line">  -v ~/.openclaw:/root/.openclaw \</span><br><span class="line">  -p 18789:18789 \</span><br><span class="line">  ghcr.io/openclaw/openclaw:latest</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr><h2 id="四、初始化配置（Onboarding）"><a href="#四、初始化配置（Onboarding）" class="headerlink" title="四、初始化配置（Onboarding）"></a>四、初始化配置（Onboarding）</h2><p>安装完成后运行：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">openclaw onboard --install-daemon</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>向导会依次询问：</p><ol><li><strong>选择模型供应商</strong> — 输入 <code>deepseek</code> &#x2F; <code>anthropic</code> &#x2F; <code>openai</code> 等</li><li><strong>输入 API Key</strong> — 粘贴你的 API Key</li><li><strong>选择默认模型</strong> — 如 <code>deepseek-v4-flash</code></li><li><strong>设置 Gateway 端口</strong> — 默认 <code>18789</code></li><li><strong>配置自动启动</strong> — 推荐设为开机自启</li></ol><p><code>--install-daemon</code> 参数会将 Gateway 注册为系统服务（macOS LaunchAgent &#x2F; Linux systemd &#x2F; Windows Scheduled Task），实现开机自启。</p><hr><h2 id="五、验证安装"><a href="#五、验证安装" class="headerlink" title="五、验证安装"></a>五、验证安装</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 确认 CLI 可用</span></span><br><span class="line">openclaw --version</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 检查 Gateway 状态</span></span><br><span class="line">openclaw gateway status</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 打开控制台</span></span><br><span class="line">openclaw dashboard</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>浏览器访问 <code>http://127.0.0.1:18789</code>，看到 Control UI 界面即为安装成功。</p><p>在聊天框发送第一条消息，如果收到 AI 回复，说明模型连接正常。</p><hr><h2 id="六、连接聊天渠道"><a href="#六、连接聊天渠道" class="headerlink" title="六、连接聊天渠道"></a>六、连接聊天渠道</h2><p>Control UI 适合桌面端调试，日常使用建议连接手机上的聊天应用。</p><h3 id="6-1-微信"><a href="#6-1-微信" class="headerlink" title="6.1 微信"></a>6.1 微信</h3><p>需要安装 <a href="https://github.com/Tencent/openclaw-weixin">OpenClaw 微信插件</a>。</p><p>快速开始：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npx -y @tencent-weixin/openclaw-weixin-cli install</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>扫码登录：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">openclaw channels login --channel openclaw-weixin</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>详见<a href="https://github.com/Tencent/openclaw-weixin/blob/main/README.zh_CN.md">README.CN.md</a></p><h3 id="6-2-Telegram"><a href="#6-2-Telegram" class="headerlink" title="6.2 Telegram"></a>6.2 Telegram</h3><ol><li>在 <a href="https://t.me/BotFather">@BotFather</a> 创建 Bot，获取 Token</li><li>配置：</li></ol><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  channels: &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    telegram: &#123;</span><br><span class="line">      enabled: true,</span><br><span class="line">      botToken: &quot;123456:ABC-DEF1234ghikl&quot;,</span><br><span class="line">      allowFrom: [&quot;@你的用户名&quot;]</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="6-3-Discord"><a href="#6-3-Discord" class="headerlink" title="6.3 Discord"></a>6.3 Discord</h3><ol><li>在 <a href="https://discord.com/developers">Discord Developer Portal</a> 创建 Bot</li><li>配置 Token 并邀请 Bot 到服务器</li><li>配置：</li></ol><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  channels: &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    discord: &#123;</span><br><span class="line">      enabled: true,</span><br><span class="line">      token: &quot;你的Bot Token&quot;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr><h2 id="七、基础配置"><a href="#七、基础配置" class="headerlink" title="七、基础配置"></a>七、基础配置</h2><p>配置文件位于 <code>~/.openclaw/openclaw.json</code>（JSON5 格式，支持注释和尾逗号）。</p><h3 id="7-1-工作区路径"><a href="#7-1-工作区路径" class="headerlink" title="7.1 工作区路径"></a>7.1 工作区路径</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  agents: &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    defaults: &#123;</span><br><span class="line">      workspace: &quot;~/.openclaw/workspace&quot;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="7-2-调整模型"><a href="#7-2-调整模型" class="headerlink" title="7.2 调整模型"></a>7.2 调整模型</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  agents: &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    defaults: &#123;</span><br><span class="line">      model: &quot;deepseek/deepseek-v4-flash&quot;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="7-3-启用网络搜索"><a href="#7-3-启用网络搜索" class="headerlink" title="7.3 启用网络搜索"></a>7.3 启用网络搜索</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  plugins: &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    entries: &#123;</span><br><span class="line">      brave: &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        config: &#123;</span><br><span class="line">          webSearch: &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            apiKey: &quot;你的API Key&quot;</span><br><span class="line">          &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">      &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="7-4-运行定时任务"><a href="#7-4-运行定时任务" class="headerlink" title="7.4 运行定时任务"></a>7.4 运行定时任务</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 设置每天 8:00 的提醒</span></span><br><span class="line">openclaw cron add \</span><br><span class="line">  --schedule <span class="string">&quot;0 8 * * *&quot;</span> \</span><br><span class="line">  --tz <span class="string">&quot;Asia/Shanghai&quot;</span> \</span><br><span class="line">  --message <span class="string">&quot;提醒晨：现在该吃药了&quot;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr><h2 id="八、常用命令"><a href="#八、常用命令" class="headerlink" title="八、常用命令"></a>八、常用命令</h2><table><thead><tr><th>命令</th><th>说明</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><code>openclaw gateway status</code></td><td>查看 Gateway 状态</td></tr><tr><td><code>openclaw gateway restart</code></td><td>重启 Gateway</td></tr><tr><td><code>openclaw gateway stop</code></td><td>停止 Gateway</td></tr><tr><td><code>openclaw dashboard</code></td><td>打开控制台</td></tr><tr><td><code>openclaw config get &lt;字段&gt;</code></td><td>读取配置</td></tr><tr><td><code>openclaw config set &lt;字段&gt; &lt;值&gt;</code></td><td>写入配置</td></tr><tr><td><code>openclaw doctor</code></td><td>诊断检查</td></tr><tr><td><code>openclaw onboard</code></td><td>重新运行配置向导</td></tr><tr><td><code>openclaw update</code></td><td>更新 OpenClaw</td></tr></tbody></table><hr><h2 id="九、安装-Skills（可选）"><a href="#九、安装-Skills（可选）" class="headerlink" title="九、安装 Skills（可选）"></a>九、安装 Skills（可选）</h2><p>Skills 是社区能力模块。在 Control UI 的 Skills 页面浏览安装，或通过 CLI：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 列出可用 Skills</span></span><br><span class="line">openclaw skills list</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 安装指定 Skill</span></span><br><span class="line">openclaw skills install &lt;skill名称&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr><h2 id="十、故障排查"><a href="#十、故障排查" class="headerlink" title="十、故障排查"></a>十、故障排查</h2><h3 id="openclaw-command-not-found"><a href="#openclaw-command-not-found" class="headerlink" title="openclaw: command not found"></a><code>openclaw: command not found</code></h3><p>npm 全局 bin 目录未在 PATH 中。解决：</p><p><strong>Windows：</strong> 将 <code>%APPDATA%\npm</code> 添加到系统环境变量 PATH 中。</p><p><strong>macOS &#x2F; Linux：</strong></p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">echo</span> <span class="string">&#x27;export PATH=&quot;$(npm prefix -g)/bin:$PATH&quot;&#x27;</span> &gt;&gt; ~/.zshrc</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">source</span> ~/.zshrc</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="Gateway-启动失败"><a href="#Gateway-启动失败" class="headerlink" title="Gateway 启动失败"></a>Gateway 启动失败</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">openclaw doctor          <span class="comment"># 诊断问题</span></span><br><span class="line">openclaw gateway logs    <span class="comment"># 查看日志</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>常见原因：</p><ul><li>端口 18789 被占用：修改 <code>gateway.port</code> 配置</li><li>API Key 无效：检查 <code>openclaw onboard</code> 中的配置</li><li>Node 版本过低：升级到 Node 22.19+</li></ul><h3 id="模型不回复"><a href="#模型不回复" class="headerlink" title="模型不回复"></a>模型不回复</h3><ol><li>确认 API Key 正确且未过期</li><li>确认账户余额充足</li><li>检查 <code>~/.openclaw/openclaw.json</code> 中 <code>agents.defaults.model</code> 配置是否正确</li><li>查看日志：<code>openclaw gateway logs</code></li></ol><hr><h2 id="进阶参考"><a href="#进阶参考" class="headerlink" title="进阶参考"></a>进阶参考</h2><ul><li><a href="https://docs.openclaw.ai/">官方文档</a></li><li><a href="https://github.com/openclaw/openclaw">GitHub 仓库</a></li><li><a href="https://docs.openclaw.ai/gateway/configuration-reference">配置参考</a></li><li><a href="https://docs.openclaw.ai/channels">所有支持的渠道</a></li><li><a href="https://docs.openclaw.ai/security">安全指南</a></li></ul>]]>
